headline: 'Change Fatigue' Ranks in Top Five Barriers to Communications and HR Success for the First Time in 2025, Reveals New Gallagher Report
summary: As companies navigate an increasingly turbulent external environment, communications and HR leaders have identified 'change fatigue' as one of the top five barriers to success, according to Gallagher's 2025 Employee Communications Report. The report, which drew insights from more than 2,000 communication and HR leaders across 55 countries, found that 44% of HR leaders view change fatigue as a key battleground for success in 2025.
